div.p:
If the President spends a maximum of five days in China, we would
                            envision: 

— the sixth day in travel to Manila;

— the seventh day in the Philippines;



— the eighth day in travel to Jakarta;

— the ninth day in Indonesia;

— the tenth day in travel to Canberra;

— the eleventh day in Australia;

— the twelfth day in travel to Wellington;

— the thirteenth day in New Zealand;

— the fourteenth and fifteenth days in travel back to the
                                    U.S.
